 muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.poster.avif?t=1726319976\" width=616 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.webm?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.mp4?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When island expand, things can get tough. You couldn't to water and havest all plants! For these issues you should use important tools.",
